column1: "Material and furniture apnara eseh ki thik korben"
"I was looking for a quotation for my flat renovation"
"How do I get appointment? Is it possible to get design by only giving measurements nd pictures?"
"Saturday day ki off day? Kau phone dhorey nah. Please provide me numbers to contact."
"Amder bashay jinish ase.. Bt aro kisu add korte cai.design kvbe bolbo?"
"Faka space or new space sara ki kaj koren?"
"Ai package e ki shudu sketch ami pabo? Sketch theke sob kichu ki amke kinte hobe"

"So the fees showing in your website is the consultation fees?\nHow do you determine the price for executing the design? I mean the furniture and fixtures... Do you build it or purchase it from readymade shops?"
"Actually I am leaving Dhaka tomorrow night"
"Ami ei bpr a ektu clear jante chascilm,,,7k er moddhei ki apnarai shob kre diye thaken."
"& when I come back to Dhaka I want to see the design as completed"
"I already talked to you about this"
"Home interior. It's a studio apartment of 750 sft."
"I would like to know more about your service. I tried to figure it out from your page, but have some queries."
"I want to see a bed room intorior design with wall fix bed and mirror almirah and wall fix vanity dressing table"
"Please make sure that they call me before Zummah."
"Thus I want to handover the design of my wardrobe to you"
"I need some of your designer to pay a visit at my place tomorrow"
"One bed room design cost koto porbe ?"
"I want to decorate my home in Bashundhara residential area. 1350 square fit. pls give your details how can we will be helpful by you."
"Actually amar problem taa likha explain kortay parbo naa"
"Ami asholay ektu phone a kotha boltay chachsilam"
"Amar netrokona te akta Bari banabo. Oitar design korabo. Apnar architect k 20 tarikh e pathano jabe?"
"Amar ekta pharmacy ache, oitar interior korabo. Amake kichu design dekhan apnader kora."
"Can you design a ceiling for a bedroom?"
